  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/58709436bebbdf120c00d7f2cb1372e7.poster.avif?t=1768781701\" width=606 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/58709436bebbdf120c00d7f2cb1372e7.webm?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/58709436bebbdf120c00d7f2cb1372e7.mp4?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br><br>Stress Ball: Confront the Stress of Jumping!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an extraordinary journey filled with excitement and challenging obstacles! \"Stress Ball\" is a 3D ball game that takes you on an adventure through thrilling courses, platforms, and demanding challenges. Immerse yourself in this unique experience and explore the world through the eyes of a bouncing ball. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Character: A Ball!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main character is a ball! However, this is no ordinary ball. It's an adventurer navigating through challenging courses and platforms by bouncing towards the goal. The control is in your hands, and thrilling moments await you!<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/445fed5ca844c77ad43afa776694c63d.poster.avif?t=1768781701\" width=606 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/445fed5ca844c77ad43afa776694c63d.webm?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/445fed5ca844c77ad43afa776694c63d.mp4?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Increasingly Challenging Levels</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Stress Ball\" introduces you to various levels that will take you away from the ordinary. Tasks that may seem simple at first become increasingly challenging as you progress. Overcome each level with skill and speed, unlock new courses, and conquer challenging obstacles. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dark Theme and Atmosphere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its depth of nuances and dark theme, \"Stress Ball\" invites you into a mysterious world. Enhanced graphics and atmospheric music promise players an immersive experience. Are you ready for this stressful journey into the dark? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/d06c469addf179a0aca82bb59bddb7f6.poster.avif?t=1768781701\" width=606 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/d06c469addf179a0aca82bb59bddb7f6.webm?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/d06c469addf179a0aca82bb59bddb7f6.mp4?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now on Steam!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stress Ball</i> is now available on Steam! Don’t miss out on this unique game! Discover the world through the eyes of a ball, navigate through challenging courses, overcome obstacles, and use your skills to reach the goal!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stress Ball</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t forget to follow our official social media accounts to stay updated on news and future updates!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/696504b46d71f41f4c49e44175e0bebf.poster.avif?t=1768781701\" width=606 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/696504b46d71f41f4c49e44175e0bebf.webm?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/696504b46d71f41f4c49e44175e0bebf.mp4?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
