muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/696504b46d71f41f4c49e44175e0bebf.poster.avif?t=1768781701\" width=606 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/696504b46d71f41f4c49e44175e0bebf.webm?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572100/extras/696504b46d71f41f4c49e44175e0bebf.mp4?t=1768781701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
